        <num>CC 937</num>
        <heading>937.  Transmission of rights of successor</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 937.  Transmission of rights of successor
The rights of a successor are transmitted to his own successors at his death, whether or not he accepted the rights, and whether or not he knew that the rights accrued to him.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
